# Local-only Maven JVM args: trust the Windows cert store so builds work behind this
# machine's Norton "Web/Mail Shield" TLS scanning. Windows-specific (WINDOWS-ROOT), so it
# must NOT be committed — it would break Linux/CI where that truststore type doesn't exist.
.mvn/jvm.config
